Privacy Policy

Thank you for using the BMI Monitor app. As privacy is of the utmost importance to us, we have created this Privacy Policy to help you understand how we collect, use, and safeguard the information you provide us with.

What Information We Collect

We do not collect any data from our users. The BMI Monitor app does not require any personal information to be entered or collected. We do not collect or store any identifiable information about our users, including their names, email addresses, phone numbers, or any other personal data.

How We Use Your Information

As we do not collect any data, we do not use any information about our users in any way.

Third-Party Access

We do not share any data with any third-party. The BMI Monitor app does not use any third-party services, such as analytics or advertising services.

Data Security

We take the security of your data very seriously. As we do not collect any data from our users, there is no data to secure. We do not store any data on our servers or any other storage device.

Changes to Our Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will post the updated Privacy Policy on our website and update the "Effective Date" at the top of the policy.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at [insert contact information].

Thank you for using the BMI Monitor app.
